    "109 This distinction makes a good example for the underlying logic used to interpret language and legal terms, especially those that are qualified as oxymora and paradoxes.",
    "In light of the complexity and oxymoronic nature of AI and related technologies, it might become necessary to apply a new (e.g., polyvalent) logic.",
